                     <interp inst="t18120916-59-off331" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120916-59-victim503" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           King
                        <interp inst="t18120916-59-victim503" type="surname" value="King"></interp>
